transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Namaste.
Executive: Namaste, haanji, haanji, haanji. Sir, mai Om baat kar raha hu aapka account manager IndiaMART se. Wo issue ke liye jo kal baat hui thi na.
Customer: Haan, haan, haan, nahi, abhi actually kya hai mai factory pahucha nahi hu.
Executive: Ji, ji, aap mere ko ya toh isi number pe call kar lijiyega ya fir aap mere ko bata dijiye mai aapko call kar lunga kis time kar sakte hain.
Customer: Toh kareeban ek ghanta maan lo aap. Hai na?
Executive: Ek ghanta. Haan. Theek hai, theek hai, theek hai sir. Mai 11 baje tak kar leta hu fir aapko mota-mota phone.
Customer: Haan, haan, haan, haan, haan.
Executive: Ji. Theek hai na? 11 baje ek baar kar lena. Actually kya hai thoda sa delay ho gaya hai.
Customer: Koi issue nahi hai sir, wo toh aapka bhi hai.
Executive: Ji, ji. Theek hai na? Mai kar leta hu sir 11 baje tak kar leta hu, koi dikkat nahi hai.
Customer: Haan, haan.
Executive: Theek hai sir. Okay sir.
